启动ConfigService&AdminService
Main Class:com.apollo-assembly#ctrip.framework.apollo.assembly.ApolloApplication
VM参数:
-Dapollo_profile=github
-Ddev_meta=http://localhost:8080/
-Dspring.datasource.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:orcl
-Dspring.datasource.username=ApolloConfig
-Dspring.datasource.password=ApolloConfig
-Deureka.instance.prefer-ip-address=true
Program参数:
--configservice --adminservice
启动PortalService:
Main Class:apollo-portal#com.ctrip.framework.apollo.portal.PortalApplication
VM 参数:
-Dapollo_profile=github,auth
-Ddev_meta=http://localhost:8080/
-Dserver.port=8070
-Dspring.datasource.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:orcl
-Dspring.datasource.username=ApolloPortal
-Dspring.datasource.password=ApolloPortal


